[Course_Description]
To sell online, you need more than a stunning website. You need to think like a marketer. Luckily, Shopify was built with marketing in mind. You can create a complete storefront without a line of code, and use the built-in marketing options to drive traffic and maximize online sales. In this course, digital marketing expert Sam Dey focuses on the marketing resources within Shopify, including email marketing, pixel retargeting, and the Shopify affiliate program. Plus, get a step-by-step guide to SEO with Shopify, and learn how to drive paid traffic to your Shopify page and use split testing to ensure your campaigns are effective. With these tips, you can ensure your Shopify store not only looks great, but sells great, too.